'''Content Gating''' is a system that allows users to filter or limit the type of content they encounter in [[Special:MyLanguage/VRChat|VRChat]]. Creators are required to label their content appropriately so that users are able to curate their experience. Content Gating settings can be adjusted from inside VRChat or the website.

==Content Warnings==
Content Warnings can be applied to either [[Special:MyLanguage/Avatars|avatars]] or [[Special:MyLanguage/Worlds|worlds]]. These are all the content warnings with usage examples:
